\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c2a17c45faecf56f0a3cb44cee4a3468e04028","tid":181794,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"其實我就是那位鬼佬，我看你們唔順眼先打你們的<br />\n<br />\np.s 我會中文"},{"pid":"c2812868e31be09a3d3d2ac10347634a0c655a20","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浪費時間</blockquote><br />\n認真對唔住，<br />\n一年一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畀自己人玩一次都好啊<br />\n<br />\n聽日開始咪又係繼續畀香港政府玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5a16f69501eb2b9c6f60b31d8f92d0ed802797","tid":181794,"uid":45850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你認真嘅話，學過散打有咩可能用叉插人塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼出拳先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840b5e4605f2502eb6de0d97caf733115bf10f20","tid":181794,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"意圖謀殺保到釋？<br />\n重新作過啦"},{"pid":"fedaa9f96547844dbf5bda4d3816d04e91e86de3","tid":181794,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"無咩可能告你意圖謀殺，頂多係意圖對身體造成嚴重傷害。<br />\n有哂人證，包括個鬼妹，證明當時係鬼佬主動襲擊你地先<br />\n你有可能可以用自衛黎defence"},{"pid":"7b5eea8e526955c9692b7e1951b161c0772596a7","tid":181794,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:50:58.000Z","msg":"認真好似用力打落頭到無論果個人大唔大隻都好有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9up"},{"pid":"993e265623119ea25290ce530a54102977500b14","tid":181794,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真好似用力打落頭到無論果個人大唔大隻都好有機會暈咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9up</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1a896b286a8bd696883d047ec44cabeb51ab2f80","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你認真嘅話，學過散打有咩可能用叉插人塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼出拳先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出拳就真係覺得無咩用。<br />\n<br />\n散打就以前學嘅，<br />\n宜家就得返個概念。<br />\n自己得個68kg，<br />\n出拳幫鬼佬撓痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1f43cc6f68aca6723981002241d5f9ad474787","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意圖謀殺保到釋？<br />\n重新作過啦</blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下年參考多啲資料。<br />\n<br />\nbtw thank you"},{"pid":"06dd28621caef3b6265db30818a6aa530ea6ebcc","tid":181794,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:53:45.000Z","msg":"打拳頭交就拳頭交啦<br />\n納武器你上去court好難解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0145862eefc587a97e34127b6851e293e9d3afb1","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無咩可能告你意圖謀殺，頂多係意圖對身體造成嚴重傷害。<br />\n有哂人證，包括個鬼妹，證明當時係鬼佬主動襲擊你地先<br />\n你有可能可以用自衛黎defence</blockquote><br />\n我一直都話鬼妹係唔信得過嘅，<br />\n佢一早人間蒸發咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拖到琴晚揾唔返條女，<br />\n班差佬先根據口供做咗結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家在場嘅就得返 Bartender, 我個朋友, 差啲畀我用叉插中嘅電源 同個鬼佬。"},{"pid":"d36a49e3aabc5a604b1fb63652921c18fc66bb1b","tid":181794,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00: