><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住<br />\n<br />\n但我相信如果我揾第二啲嘢黎玩，<br />\n你都會照樣入黎講返同樣嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd13efdf4303a8f754544c72a8a65a560112d88d","tid":181794,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心左tim 屌你"},{"pid":"e13e6001f34ce19c84b086df678c19d25399cd19","tid":181794,"uid":28180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"應該無蓄意傷害他人身體罪架喎，一係就傷人，一係就意圖造成身體嚴重傷害<br />\n同埋意圖謀殺重出到黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw讀得書少，愚人節快樂"},{"pid":"3f93251e20c50b8cb43e06b472e05c6996350838","tid":181794,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"冇CCTV有人證拿掛"},{"pid":"fdaabd0b25cb53e3bf095937666194e0f7a856ef","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心左tim 屌你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先講聲對唔住<br />\n我只係四月一先出黎玩。<br />\n希望唔好令到巴打當《狼來了》，<br />\n連登仔應該互相幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092796e32cb743b49979703436a66593e5ef00e5","tid":181794,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"愚人節快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵律師然後同佢傾啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個post都唔知會唔會俾人拎做證據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵律師記得貨比三家 , 打多幾間問下價<br />\ngoogle下律師個名睇下有冇伏"},{"pid":"d276a347e0429bf5605b987d91482b59012fb437","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該無蓄意傷害他人身體罪架喎，一係就傷人，一係就意圖造成身體嚴重傷害<br />\n同埋意圖謀殺重出到黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw讀得書少，愚人節快樂</blockquote><br />\n其實我就覺得以一個外行人嘅敘述方式去講嘅話可能比較會容易令人信服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有bug係真嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴打有興趣嘅話可以參考《香港法例》第212章《傷害人身罪條例》中嘅第10條、第17條同第19條<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/212/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F212%2F&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF08n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b26f87c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/chi/hk/legis/ord/212/</a>"},{"pid":"373cf7ff80abbc5dde413039d1f891083f7fdb48","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇CCTV有人證拿掛</blockquote><br />\n有<br />\n電源同我朋友就是人證<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50dc6aef72a17de095918d66df26a0d4b2df012","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愚人節快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵律師然後同佢傾啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個post都唔知會唔會俾人拎做證據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵律師記得貨比三家 , 打多幾間問下價<br />\ngoogle下律師個名睇下有冇伏</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我時日無多，<br />\n最後分分鐘連屎都要照食......<br />\n<br />\nbtw 愚人節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cc72f0dff85fbaa266adfa99ab4b2f64f05298","tid":181794,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愚人節快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵律師然後同佢傾啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=