=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea12b056fc89209b77837ff83a6014786998ba7","tid":181794,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>進入司法程序就最好唔好上黎討論啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔想坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲要移民<br />\n<br />\n原本諗住考慮要唔要揾謝偉俊，<br />\n但條撚樣報價真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪叫你唔好上黎討論<br />\n去搵律師傾啦</blockquote><br />\n出面律師好貴，<br />\n想先睇下情況先決定用唔用免費嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢單罪真係太大，我無法承受</blockquote><br />\n傾家盪產都要揾個好律師。 老謀唔係講笑。 唔好諗住衰左第一審先揾個好D既上訴， 壞左個頭好難兜。"},{"pid":"9b3f81cced98b2c0db0153157d6cf283bb7c74b1","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲話出拳冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個hook打落佢下巴佢90kg都訓低啦<br />\n仲要佢醉醉地 頸部肌肉都鎖唔實<br />\n仲要話救人心切拎刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無信心嘅嘢我係唔會做。<br />\n<br />\n特別係呢啲危急關頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔知搞唔搞得佢掂嘅時候，<br />\n一定係揾人/工具黎對付<br />\n<br />\nbtw我係拎叉唔係刀，<br />\n餐刀都唔利<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da9c232f87282e86bccd05aeedf0d3cb57cb771","tid":181794,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>進入司法程序就最好唔好上黎討論啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔想坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲要移民<br />\n<br />\n原本諗住考慮要唔要揾謝偉俊，<br />\n但條撚樣報價真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪叫你唔好上黎討論<br />\n去搵律師傾啦</blockquote><br />\n出面律師好貴，<br />\n想先睇下情況先決定用唔用免費嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 